<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_01_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema611_01.css" />
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_01_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2 flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 3-2』 분수 알아보기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_brown"><span class="empty_box nemo"></span></span><span lang="y" class="ml-6">&nbsp;안에 알맞은 수를 써넣어 크기가 같은 분수를 만들어 보세요.</span></h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_30">
          <div class="input_area box1">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_10">
              <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>7</span></div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="14" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>21</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>8</span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="28" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="input_area box2">
            <div class="flex align_center gap_10">
              <div class="fraction_box"><span>12</span><span>24</span></div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>12</span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="8" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve top0">
                <p lang="y">분모와 분자에 각각 0이 아닌 같은 수를 곱하면 크기가 같은 분수가 됩니다.</p>
                <div class="lines_img top">
                  <span class="line_txt1">×2</span>
                  <span class="line_txt2">×3</span>
                  <span class="line_txt3">×4</span>
                </div>
                <p class="flex align_center gap_10 mt_1">
                  ➔
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>7</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>14</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>6</span><span>21</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>8</span><span>28</span></span>
                </p>
                <div class="lines_img bottom mt_1">
                  <span class="line_txt1">×2</span>
                  <span class="line_txt2">×3</span>
                  <span class="line_txt3">×4</span>
                </div>
                <p lang="y">분모와 분자를 각각 0이 아닌 같은 수로 나누면 크기가 같은 분수가 됩니다.</p>
                <div class="lines_img top ">
                  <span class="line_txt1">÷2</span>
                  <span class="line_txt2">÷3</span>
                  <span class="line_txt3">÷4</span>
                </div>
                <p class="flex align_center gap_10 mt_1">
                  ➔
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>12</span><span>24</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>6</span><span>12</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>28</span></span>
                  =
                  <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>6</span></span>
                </p>
                <div class="lines_img bottom mt_1">
                  <span class="line_txt1">÷2</span>
                  <span class="line_txt2">÷3</span>
                  <span class="line_txt3">÷4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
